{"tid":2518194,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情將完結的時候除了黃藍絲之外，將會出現多2批人","createTime":"2021-05-06T00:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T00:50:40.000Z","uid":155431,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6f7513698c7c8d289f9e30a43ee883b309589e49","tid":2518194,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:31:14.000Z","msg":"第一批係口罩撚，覺得打左針有得醫都好，佢都好相信口罩可以為佢帶來保護。就算疫情完結都好，佢地都會繼續戴口罩，佢地主張戴口罩可以預防埋傷風感冒，而且會歧視唔戴口罩出街嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n第二批係主張唔洗再戴口罩嘅人，認為既然疫情就完，打晒針又有得醫，點解仲要戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n呢2班人會不斷互相攻擊同批鬥，甚至最對方拍照放上網公審。直到疫情真正完結，口罩令都冇埋，呢2班人都會繼續互相對罵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n預計1年-2年後會出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4fce84ae8cc9bea527316545bc67a5c7f6ebfd","tid":2518194,"uid":258948,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:32:33.000Z","msg":"有啲女戴左罩個陣望落唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但一除左罩就<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁俾我老閪都話要帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b87bc01d7f151f18ea46ca4b7f98c9738b89e7","tid":2518194,"uid":105486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6a4fce84ae8cc9bea527316545bc67a5c7f6ebfd","tid":2518194,"uid":258948,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:32:33.000Z","msg":"有啲女戴左罩個陣望落唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但一除左罩就<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁俾我老閪都話要帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:35:04.000Z","msg":"男都係啦"},{"pid":"d59bf9757685288b862971c8d8ff91b644809819","tid":2518194,"uid":25794,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:35:40.000Z","msg":"傻啦 有禁蒙面法架嘛<br />\n點戴口罩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha